I want to serve him.

00:30:25.272 --> 00:30:26.674
I want to put my faith in him.

00:30:26.754 --> 00:30:28.296
I want to be committed to him.

00:30:28.777 --> 00:30:30.961
I want to live the life he wants me to live.

00:30:31.381 --> 00:30:39.173
I want to remove all limitations from God so God can do what he wants to do in my life exceedingly, abundantly, above all I could ask a thing.

00:30:39.834 --> 00:30:41.457
Or pastor, I'm a believer already.

00:30:42.158 --> 00:30:44.221
Pastor, today I need to reset my faith.

00:30:44.902 --> 00:30:46.485
I need to reexamine my habits.

00:30:47.066 --> 00:30:49.189
I need to look at, am I reading my one-year Bible?

00:30:49.750 --> 00:30:51.012
Have I developed that habit?

00:30:51.893 --> 00:30:53.135
Am I writing in my journal?

00:30:53.215 --> 00:30:54.898
Have I developed that habit?

00:30:55.170 --> 00:30:56.591
If you haven't, pick it up today.

00:30:56.651 --> 00:30:59.634
If you started, dropped it, it's okay.

00:30:59.975 --> 00:31:00.835
Just pick it up today.

00:31:01.296 --> 00:31:02.617
But you say, pastor, pray for me.

00:31:03.138 --> 00:31:05.500
So if that's you, let's all pray this together.

00:31:05.520 --> 00:31:06.761
Sit with me, Heavenly Father.

00:31:07.362 --> 00:31:08.062
I am a sinner.

00:31:09.043 --> 00:31:13.848
I believe that Jesus Christ is the Son of God, that He died for me and He rose again.

00:31:14.609 --> 00:31:17.191
Jesus, come into my life, come into my heart.

00:31:17.551 --> 00:31:21.976
I receive you now as my Lord and my Savior.

00:31:21.996 --> 00:31:24.498
Fill me with the Holy Spirit and take my life.

00:31:24.642 --> 00:31:25.523
and make a difference.

00:31:25.923 --> 00:31:28.727
In Jesus' name, amen.

00:31:30.008 --> 00:31:32.251
Thanks for watching this week's message.

00:31:32.931 --> 00:31:36.616
One way for you to connect here at Church on the Rock is through the God is for you classes.

00:31:37.256 --> 00:31:45.085
These classes are designed to teach you about the culture, mission, and values of Church on the Rock, and about your God given design.

00:31:45.926 --> 00:31:52.754
You can take these classes anytime by going to our website at cltr.org slash God is for you.

00:31:53.122 --> 00:32:00.707
And if you want to know about all the incredible things we have here at Church on Rock, make sure to visit our website at COTR.org.

00:32:01.529 --> 00:32:04.178
And never forget, God is for you.
